\c 32
\s INkosi elungileyo
\p
\v 1 Khangela, inkosi izabusa ngokulunga\x + Hlab. 45.1. 72.1,2,4. Jer. 23.5.\x*, leziphathamandla zibuse ngesahlulelo.
\v 2 Lomuntu uzakuba njengendawo yokucatshela umoya lesivikelo kuzulu lesiphepho\x + 4.6. 25.4.\x*; njengemifula yamanzi endaweni eyomileyo\x + 25.5.\x*, njengomthunzi\x + 4.6. 25.4.\x* wedwala elikhulu elizweni elomileyo\x + Hlab. 63.1.\x*.
\v 3 Lamehlo\x + 35.5.\x* alabo ababonayo kawayikufiphala, lezindlebe\x + 35.5.\x* zalabo abezwayo zizalalela.
\v 4 Lenhliziyo yabalamawala izaqedisisa ulwazi, lolimi lwabagagasayo\x + 28.11. 35.6.\x* luzaphangisa ukukhuluma ngokucaca.
\v 5 Isithutha kasisayikubizwa \add ngokuthi\add* sihloniphekile, loncitshanayo angathiwa uyaphana.
\v 6 Ngoba isithutha sikhuluma ubuthutha, lenhliziyo yaso isebenze okubi, ukwenza ubuzenzisi, lokukhuluma okuphambeneyo ngeN\nd kosi\nd*, ukwenza umphefumulo wolambileyo ube ze, senze kusweleke okunathwayo kowomileyo.
\v 7 Izikhali zoncitshanayo lazo zimbi; yena uceba amacebo akhohlakeleyo ukuze achithe abayanga\x + 13.5.\x* ngamazwi amanga, lanxa oswelayo ekhuluma okulungileyo.
\v 8 Kodwa ohloniphekayo uceba izinto ezihloniphekayo\x + Jobe 30.15.\x*; langezinto ezihloniphekayo yena uzakuma.
\s Ukuxwayiswa kwabesifazana beJerusalema
\p
\v 9 Vukani, besifazana abonwabileyo\x + 3.16-24. 32.11,18. Amos 6.1.\x*, lizwe ilizwi lami; madodakazi avikelekileyo, bekani indlebe ekukhulumeni kwami.
\v 10 Izinsuku ezedlula umnyaka lizathuthumela, besifazana abavikelekileyo, ngoba ukuvunwa kwevini kuzaphela, ukubutha kakuyikufika.
\v 11 Thuthumelani, besifazana abonwabileyo\x + 3.16-24. 32.11,18. Amos 6.1.\x*, liqhuqhe, bavikelekileyo; khululani, lizinqunule\x + 47.2,3.\x*, libhince \add amasaka\add* enkalweni\x + 3.24. 1 Kho. 20.31.\x*.
\v 12 Bazakhalela amabele \add okumunya\add*, amasimu amahle, ivini elithelayo\x + Hlab. 128.3. Hez. 19.10.\x*.
\v 13 Phezu komhlabathi wabantu bami kuzakhula ameva \add lo\add*khula oluhlabayo\x + 34.13. Hos. 9.6.\x*; yebo, phezu kwezindlu zonke zenjabulo, \add e\add*mzi\add ni\add* wentokozo\x + 22.2.\x*.
\v 14 Ngoba isigodlo sizadelwa\x + 27.10.\x*, inengi lomuzi lizatshiywa; inqaba lemiphotshongo\x + 2 Lan. 27.3.\x* kuzakuba yimihome kuze kube phakade, intokozo yabobabhemi beganga, \add l\add*amadlelo emihlambi\x + 27.10.\x*;
\v 15 aze athululelwe phezu kwethu uMoya\x + Jow. 2.28.\x* evela phezulu, lenkangala\x + 35.1,2.\x* ibe yinsimu ethelayo, lensimu ethelayo ithiwe lihlathi\x + 29.17.\x*.
\v 16 Khona isahlulelo sizahlala enkangala, lokulunga kuhlale ensimini ethelayo\x + 29.17.\x*.
\v 17 Lomsebenzi wokulunga\x + Jak. 3.18. Hlab. 72.3. Roma 5.1.\x* uzakuba yikuthula\x + Hlab. 119.165.\x*, lokwenza kokulunga\x + 22.2.\x* kube yikuthula lokuqinisekiswa kuze kube nininini.
\v 18 Labantu bami bazahlala endaweni yokuhlala elokuthula, lezindaweni zokuhlala ezivikelekileyo, lezindaweni zokuphumula ezonwabileyo\x + 3.16-24. 32.11,18. Amos 6.1.\x*.
\v 19 Kodwa lizakuna ngesiqhotho\x + 28.2.\x* ekwehleni\x + Zek. 11.2.\x* kwehlathi\x + 9.18. 10.18,19. Hez. 31.18.\x*, lomuzi uzathotshiswa endaweni ephansi.
\v 20 Libusisiwe lina elihlanyela ngasemanzini wonke\x + Tshu. 11.1.\x*, lithumezela\x + Jobe 21.11.\x* \add lapho\add* inyawo zezinkabi labobabhemi\x + 30.24.\x*.